==English==

===Etymology===
[F. gerbille. Cf. Jerboa.] 
===Noun===
'''gerbil''' ([[gerbils]])
#(Zoöl.) One of several species of small, jumping, [[murine]] [[rodent]]s, of the genus ''[[Gerbillus]]''. In their leaping powers they resemble the [[jerboa]]. They inhabit Africa, India, and Southern Europe.
====Related terms====
*[[gerbilling]], [[gerbiling]]


